    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring Me Hope is an <strong>adventure RPG</strong>,  drawing inspiration from titles such as <i>Undertale</i> and <i>Enter The Gungeon</i>. This is a <strong>story rich</strong> experience about love, life, and connection. Sink into the unique and bittersweet life of Alium.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1493290/extras/b1631c839f3127eb7a249002c84f873c.poster.avif?t=1763667918\" width=800 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1493290/extras/b1631c839f3127eb7a249002c84f873c.webm?t=1763667918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1493290/extras/b1631c839f3127eb7a249002c84f873c.mp4?t=1763667918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Handmade Experience</strong> - Created with love and care put into every pixel.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Overcome the Odds </strong>- High stakes and fast paced. Parry, dodge, or overpower your enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Evolve and Experiment </strong>- Set grass on fire, electrify wet enemies, or use oil to create an explosive chain reaction. Items can interact with fluids, objects, and enemies leading to unexpected results. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Heartfelt Story</strong> - An emotional adventure that will take you from the bottom of the ocean through cities and between planes of existence.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fiendish Foes</strong> - Powerful and unique boss fights will challenge you to hone your skills and formulate new strategies. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>More than Meets the Eye</strong> - Discover an unreasonable amount of hidden bosses and areas to explore.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customize your gameplay </strong>- Modify your game to fit your preferences! Minimize screenshake, max out the difficulty, and more.</p></li></ul>",
